    [Abbadomon Core] from your hand or trash to your empty breeding area without
    paying the cost.\n[End of All Turns] [Once Per Turn] By placing 1 level 6 or
    lower Digimon card with [Negamon]\_in its text from your trash as this Digimon's
    top digivolution card, delete 1 of your opponent's Digimon with the same level
    as the placed card."
